agent. Statistics Avg. AB R H 2B 3B HR RBI BB SO SB Slg. OBP
</P>
<P>
   Tulsa .309 433 79 134 32 3 18 75 30 56 18 .522 .371 Charlotte
.000 4 0 0 0 0 0 1 0 1 0 .000 .000
</P>
<P>
   Mateo overcame a one-month stint on the disabled list when he
separated his left shoulder in mid-April.
</P>
<P>
   ``Obviously, every now and then, you're fortunate to have an
individual who is exceptionally talented,'' Rangers assistant
general manager Dan O'Brien said, ``and while Ruben Mateo certainly
fits that classification, it's a little unfair to him at this
juncture in his career as a Double-A outfielder to label him as an
impact player.
</P>
<P>
   ``He certainly has the potential to be that, but you've
obviously got to have some patience in allowing him to work his way
up here, get established and let his talent take him to whatever
level he is capable of.''
