from opponents during the exhibition season. Great along the line
of scrimmage on both sides of the ball. Addition of Harbaugh and
his infectious feistiness has put some zip into the offense. Front
seven on defense, headed by outside linebacker Peter Boulware and
inside backer Ray Lewis, can play with anyone in the league.
</P>
