<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-04 15:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9543 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-YOUTH-MOVEMENT-HNS &LR;      09-04 0498
