<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CLINTON PRAISES AHERN, IRELAND ECONOMIC GROWTH AS FACTOR IN
PEACE
 &HT;    By BERT ROUGHTON JR. 
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
