<DOCNO> NYT19980904.0280 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-04 17:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0083 &Cx1f; tad-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPOT-BJT-COX05update     09-04 1469
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT-BJT-COX05 </SLUG>
