<P>
   Houston at Arizona, 7:35 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   San Francisco at Los Angeles, 8:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Monday, Sept. 7 Milwaukee at Pittsburgh, 1:35 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Atlanta at N.Y. Mets, 1:40 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Chicago Cubs at St. Louis, 2:10 p.m.
</P>
<P>
   Florida at Colorado, 3:05 p.m.
</P>
<P>
