<P>
   &UR; SPORTS EDITORS, PHOTO EDITORS:  &LR; The New York Yankees are in in
the midst of a historic season. They have a chance of winning the
most games in the history of baseball, both in total games and in
terms of percentage.
</P>
<P>
   Because of the growing importance of each game, and the rising
interest in the team across the country, the New York Times News
Service is now providing enhanced photo coverage.
</P>
<P>
   We will move at least one picture _ or more, depending on
developments _ from each Yankee home game for the rest of the
season. These pictures will be moving late in the cycle if
necessary, something we have not previously provided.
</P>
<P>
   As the season moves toward completion, we will also have photo
coverage of selected Yankee games away from New York.
</P>
<P>
