<P>
   Auto Stories: &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ABOUT-CARS-ISUZU (Undated) _ The new 1998 Isuzu Amigo (the old
model rode into the sunset in 1994) still comes with a canvas top
and soft plastic windows in the back. But a hard-roof option is due
this summer, as a 1999 model. Moreover, both the softtop and
hardtop versions offer more of what appealed to buyers of the old
Amigo, plus an optional dose of muscle and luxury. By Peter
Passell. (Moved). Photo.
</P>
<P>
   CAR-SMART-KIA (Undated) _ It's cheap, it's cute and the top
comes off: What's not to like? Too much, alas. For while the 1999
Kia Sportage two-door convertible from Korea is certainly ready to
deliver fun, for the beach-blanket crowd, there's no mistaking it
for the more polished, car-like miniature sport utilities from
Japan. By Peter Passell. (Moved). Photo.
</P>
