<HEADLINE>
6 CHILDREN FOUND STRANGLED AFTER MOTHER CONFESSES TO 911
</HEADLINE>
   (jw) 
 By DIRK JOHNSON   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
